To call a method `m` on a superclass, parentheses are needed after the keyword super (e.g., `super().m()`).

frontmatter.shortDescription: To call a method on a superclass, parentheses are needed after the keyword super
frontmatter.shortCorrection: To call a method on a superclass, it is wrong to write parentheses after the keyword super
